column5: Ahhhhhhh never mind,it was just Italy scoring a goal.
That should screw my drive home going into Woodbridge!
For some reason,I cant do a full edit Rob.LOL
And here I thought North York had finally been swallowed up into the bowels of the earth.
Freudian slip...this is more of a quack than a quake.
How did they make time from rolling around on the ground grabbing at thier shins and wincing in pain long enough to score a gooooaaaaaallllll?? ??
And here I thought this was going to be a post about the G8 summit...
No, G8 is not earth shattering.
Just a little tactical sideplay to distract the ref long enough while they drug the opposing goaltender
